 class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 30, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mdn1665703132645.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mdn1665703132645.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mdn1665703132645.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mdn1665703132645\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__ugethwnd_403377\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the window handle of the Uniface main application window.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__topic_d120278e1_d120279e1_d120280e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mdn1665703132645_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__codeblock_cyr_kyz_zvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;windows.h&gt;\n\nHWND ugethwnd ();</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__topic_d85557e1_d85558e1_d85559e1_d85560e1_d85561e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d363799e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__d6420e20\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__topic_d85562e1_d85563e1_d85564e1_d85565e1_d85566e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d363799e70\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__p_d120296e1_d120297e1_d120298e1\">The window handle of the calling Uniface\n            application window.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__topic_d85567e1_d85568e1_d85569e1_d85570e1_d85571e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d363799e79\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__d6421e20\">Microsoft Windows platforms only. In library\n          <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>. </p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__topic_d85572e1_d85573e1_d85574e1_d85575e1_d85576e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d363799e92\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__p_d120308e1_d120309e1_d120310e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ugethwnd</code> returns the window handle\n            of the application window of the calling Uniface application. This handle can be used in\n            subsequent Microsoft Windows API calls, for instance the <code class=\"ph codeph\">SetWindowText</code>\n            function. The type <code class=\"ph codeph\">HWND</code> is defined in the include file\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">windows.h</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__p_d120311e1_d120312e1_d120313e1\">For example, code that uses\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugethwnd</code> (see the example provided with\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugetname</code>).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__section_zdg_4yz_zvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d363799e121\">Example: ugetname and ugethwnd</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugethwnd</code> and\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugetname</code> to obtain the Uniface application window handle and title.\n            It then changes the application title a couple of times (implementing a simple progress\n            indicator) and finally restores it back to its original value.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mdn1665703132645_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mdn1665703132645__codeblock_shv_pyz_zvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n#include &lt;windows.h&gt;\n\nEXPORT void PHASECOUNTER ()\n{\nHWND hApp;\nchar name[201];\nchar txt[50];\nint i;\n\nhApp = ugethwnd(); /* Get application window handle */\nugetname(hApp, name, sizeof(name)-1); /* Get window title */\n\nfor ( i=1; i&lt;10; i++ ) /* During 10 seconds ... */\n{\nsprintf(txt, \"Phase %d of 10\", i);\nSetWindowText(hApp, txt); /* Change application window title */\nSleep(1000); /* Pause 1 second */\n}\n\nSetWindowText(hApp, name); /* Restore application window title*/\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529866\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529866\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ugethwnd Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 30, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return the window handle of the Uniface main application window. Explain this code #include <windows.h> HWND ugethwnd (); Copy Parameters None Return Values The window handle of the calling Uniface application window. Use Microsoft Windows platforms only. In library yrtl . Description ugethwnd returns the window handle of the application window of the calling Uniface application. This handle can be used in subsequent Microsoft Windows API calls, for instance the SetWindowText function. The type HWND is defined in the include file windows.h For example, code that uses ugethwnd (see the example provided with ugetname ). Example: ugetname and ugethwnd The following example uses ugethwnd and ugetname to obtain the Uniface application window handle and title. It then changes the application title a couple of times (implementing a simple progress indicator) and finally restores it back to its original value. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> #include <windows.h> EXPORT void PHASECOUNTER () { HWND hApp; char name[201]; char txt[50]; int i; hApp = ugethwnd(); /* Get application window handle */ ugetname(hApp, name, sizeof(name)-1); /* Get window title */ for ( i=1; i<10; i++ ) /* During 10 seconds ... */ { sprintf(txt, \"Phase %d of 10\", i); SetWindowText(hApp, txt); /* Change application window title */ Sleep(1000); /* Pause 1 second */ } SetWindowText(hApp, name); /* Restore application window title*/ } Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}